**Cooldown Class**
================

### Description

A cooldown class that can be used to prevent actions from being performed too frequently.

### Code

```javascript
class Cooldown {
  /**
   * Creates a new cooldown instance.
   * @param {number} duration - The duration of the cooldown in milliseconds.
   */
  constructor(duration) {
    this.duration = duration;
    this.lastActivation = null;
  }

  /**
   * Checks if the cooldown has expired.
   * @returns {boolean} True if the cooldown has expired, false otherwise.
   */
  hasExpired() {
    const now = Date.now();
    if (this.lastActivation === null) {
      return true;
    }
    return now - this.lastActivation >= this.duration;
  }

  /**
   * Resets the cooldown.
   */
  reset() {
    this.lastActivation = null;
  }

  /**
   * Activates the cooldown.
   */
  activate() {
    this.lastActivation = Date.now();
  }
}

